pl_output:
Welcome to the Alicebot Account Manager. From here, you can view your current +standings+ in all Alicebot services, most notably the Alicebot casino.
You can also +redeem+ codes for `TABC` to use throughout the in-game Alicebot system. These codes can be obtained from giveaways or dtr.haunty_mall.
In addition, you can deposit GC into `TABC` at a rate of 10KGC to `A1``TABC` with +deposit+ or +withdraw+ at the same rate.
To perform these actions, do alicebot.account {action:""} with your desired +action+.
(For a script friendly, fast way of depositing: alicebot.depositfast `JMIDSEC`)
